305
00:12:49,460 --> 00:12:51,380
So every time I was about to spike,

306
00:12:51,380 --> 00:12:52,440
when I saw her,

307
00:12:54,500 --> 00:12:55,340
I would instinctively

308
00:12:56,860 --> 00:12:59,600
avoid her and get scared.

309
00:13:01,380 --> 00:13:02,880
That's my biggest problem.

310
00:13:04,620 --> 00:13:05,920
You need to learn from me.

311
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:07,620
