319
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:24,340
and you

320
00:13:24,500 --> 00:13:26,280
will work on your mental issues.

321
00:13:27,060 --> 00:13:28,060
Let's work hard together.

322
00:13:28,060 --> 00:13:28,900
