420
00:17:37,100 --> 00:17:38,120
You're quite the talented one.

421
00:17:38,380 --> 00:17:39,400
Making great progress.

422
00:17:53,620 --> 00:17:55,120
When facing my weaknesses,

423
00:17:55,460 --> 00:17:56,860
I have to bravely overcome them.

424
00:17:56,860 --> 00:17:57,760
I have to face them,

425
00:17:57,980 --> 00:17:59,220
so I can change

426
00:17:59,220 --> 00:18:00,440
and become stronger.

427
00:18:01,260 --> 00:18:02,100
Chen Weilan.

428
00:18:02,420 --> 00:18:04,240
Volleyball is about winning.

429
00:18:04,780 --> 00:18:06,760
But before you beat others,

430
00:18:07,140 --> 00:18:09,080
