435
00:18:41,660 --> 00:18:43,440
Why are you getting up? Stay in bed.

436
00:18:44,420 --> 00:18:45,280
Lie down.

437
00:18:45,820 --> 00:18:46,780
Slow down. Take it easy.

438
00:18:46,780 --> 00:18:47,620
Slow down.

439
00:18:52,340 --> 00:18:53,220
- It's okay.
- Are you okay?

440
00:18:53,220 --> 00:18:54,060
I'll be fine after a rest.

441
00:18:54,620 --> 00:18:55,520
It's okay.

442
00:18:56,020 --> 00:18:56,860
