445
00:19:05,300 --> 00:19:06,680
Your mom's right.

446
00:19:07,900 --> 00:19:08,820
I'm lying here

447
00:19:08,820 --> 00:19:10,120
like a useless person.

448
00:19:11,380 --> 00:19:13,340
The business is suffering,

449
00:19:13,340 --> 00:19:15,080
and your training is being delayed.

450
00:19:16,100 --> 00:19:17,080
It's really causing trouble.

451
00:19:17,700 --> 00:19:19,160
Don't worry about it.

452
00:19:19,380 --> 00:19:20,340
Since you're lying here,

453
00:19:20,340 --> 00:19:21,460
just rest well.

454
00:19:21,460 --> 00:19:23,360
Think of it as taking a vacation.

455
00:19:23,520 --> 00:19:24,920
I've got things under control with the team.

456
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:25,820
I'm the captain.

457
00:19:25,820 --> 00:19:26,660
Rest assured.

458
00:19:29,780 --> 00:19:31,080
I'm not worried about others.

459
00:19:31,860 --> 00:19:33,280
I'm worried about you, the captain.

460
00:19:34,300 --> 00:19:35,140
You're always

461
00:19:35,580 --> 00:19:36,680
so headstrong.

462
00:19:37,100 --> 00:19:38,860
You'd be better off
helping your mom skewer meat.

463
00:19:38,860 --> 00:19:41,220
Dad, didn't we agree?

464
00:19:41,220 --> 00:19:42,620
During this year,

465
00:19:42,620 --> 00:19:43,540
