466
00:19:43,540 --> 00:19:44,620
I play my beach volleyball.

467
00:19:44,620 --> 00:19:45,760
We don't interfere with each other.

468
00:19:46,020 --> 00:19:47,080
Of course, I remember.

469
00:19:47,500 --> 00:19:48,560
But I'm telling you.

470
00:19:49,300 --> 00:19:50,920
This six months is almost up.

471
00:19:55,100 --> 00:19:56,100
I came today

472
00:19:56,100 --> 00:19:58,240
