486
00:20:22,990 --> 00:20:25,040
to the young players with more potential.

487
00:20:26,700 --> 00:20:27,720
It's really him.

488
00:20:29,220 --> 00:20:30,840
Uncle Li, do you know Coach Lu?

489
00:20:31,540 --> 00:20:32,660
