490
00:20:32,660 --> 00:20:34,480
He's the National Youth Team coach.

491
00:20:35,780 --> 00:20:37,440
Twenty years ago, we were partners.

492
00:20:40,540 --> 00:20:41,920
We were evenly matched,

493
00:20:43,340 --> 00:20:45,000
