496
00:20:48,980 --> 00:20:50,200
It's nothing to talk about.

497
00:20:51,500 --> 00:20:52,860
We were old partners

498
00:20:52,860 --> 00:20:54,880
and played together for a long time.

499
00:20:55,700 --> 00:20:56,980
I don't dwell on past glories.

500
00:20:56,980 --> 00:20:57,820
Don't you know that?

501
00:20:58,100 --> 00:20:59,720
