Who is it?

573
00:24:39,980 --> 00:24:40,880
Hello, property management.

574
00:24:41,380 --> 00:24:42,220
Don't open it.

575
00:24:45,780 --> 00:24:46,620
You...

576
00:24:46,640 --> 00:24:47,640
Which one of you is Lu Xiaole?

577
00:24:51,620 --> 00:24:52,460
Lu Xiaole?

578
00:24:52,820 --> 00:24:53,660
It's you, right?

579
00:24:54,660 --> 00:24:55,680
It's so late,

580
00:24:56,180 --> 00:24:57,480
and you're still sleeping on the sofa?

581
00:24:58,940 --> 00:24:59,780
Lu Xiaole,

582
00:24:59,940 --> 00:25:01,420
you owe Mr. Bao a million yuan,

583
00:25:01,420 --> 00:25:02,360
and it's due.

584
00:25:03,060 --> 00:25:03,900
Pay up.

585
00:25:06,340 --> 00:25:07,280
Get up, get up.

586
00:25:07,940 --> 00:25:09,540
Nice to meet you.

587
00:25:09,940 --> 00:25:11,040
How about a drink?

588
00:25:12,300 --> 00:25:13,340
No drinks.

589
00:25:13,340 --> 00:25:14,260
Stop it.

590
00:25:14,260 --> 00:25:15,520
- Just pay up.
- No money.

591
00:25:15,860 --> 00:25:16,700
No money?

592
00:25:16,980 --> 00:25:17,820
Come on.

593
00:25:18,420 --> 00:25:19,660
Well. Rest assured.

594
00:25:20,260 --> 00:25:21,100
I'm his cousin.

595
00:25:21,580 --> 00:25:23,040
I'll make sure he pays up.

596
00:25:24,500 --> 00:25:25,960
We're professionals at collecting debts.

597
00:25:26,540 --> 00:25:28,440
We have countless ways to deal

598
00:25:29,020 --> 00:25:30,280
with people like you who don't pay.

599
00:25:30,620 --> 00:25:31,480
I know.

600
00:25:32,420 --> 00:25:34,480
I've seen your methods.

601
00:25:40,620 --> 00:25:41,960
Let me explain again.

602
00:25:42,300 --> 00:25:43,140
Well.

603
00:25:43,820 --> 00:25:44,760
A few years ago,

604
00:25:45,500 --> 00:25:46,620
I invested

605
00:25:46,620 --> 00:25:48,570
in a robotic vacuum startup.

606
00:25:48,980 --> 00:25:49,840
The company

607
00:25:50,340 --> 00:25:52,400
has been acquired by a large corporation.

608
00:25:53,820 --> 00:25:55,300
In a month,

609
00:25:55,300 --> 00:25:57,000
they'll distribute a million yuan in dividends.

610
00:25:57,340 --> 00:25:58,580
Your money isn't a problem.

611
00:25:58,580 --> 00:26:00,160
Enough talk.

612
00:26:00,700 --> 00:26:01,740
All this talk

613
00:26:01,740 --> 00:26:03,080
just means

614
00:26:03,340 --> 00:26:04,780
you don't want to pay, right?

615
00:26:04,780 --> 00:26:06,100
No, no, no.

616
00:26:06,100 --> 00:26:07,480
No? Then pay up.

617
00:26:08,140 --> 00:26:09,840
This is our first visit,

618
00:26:10,420 --> 00:26:11,400
so we're being nice.

619
00:26:11,900 --> 00:26:12,740
Three days.

620
00:26:13,300 --> 00:26:14,980
If we don't see the money in three days...

621
00:26:14,980 --> 00:26:15,920
Okay, three days.

622
00:26:16,580 --> 00:26:17,540
Three days.

623
00:26:17,540 --> 00:26:18,380
No problem.

624
00:26:18,980 --> 00:26:20,160
It's settled then.

625
00:26:20,420 --> 00:26:21,400
Well.

626
00:26:21,660 --> 00:26:22,500
You two

627
00:26:22,500 --> 00:26:23,480
can go now.

628
00:26:23,860 --> 00:26:24,880
Go to the next place.

629
00:26:25,220 --> 00:26:26,060
Three days.

630
00:26:26,100 --> 00:26:26,940
Three days.

631
00:26:26,980 --> 00:26:27,820
- Three days.
- Okay.

632
00:26:32,780 --> 00:26:33,680
Thank you.

633
00:26:39,180 --> 00:26:40,300
Modern people complain

634
00:26:40,300 --> 00:26:41,420
that life moves fast.

635
00:26:41,420 --> 00:26:42,260
Can't we slow down?

636
00:26:42,260 --> 00:26:44,020
It's just a month. Is it long?

637
00:26:44,020 --> 00:26:45,320
They said three days.

638
00:26:46,100 --> 00:26:47,200
Think about it.

639
00:26:48,300 --> 00:26:49,140
Daxing.

640
00:26:50,380 --> 00:26:52,420
Stop nagging.

641
00:26:52,420 --> 00:26:55,100
I'll handle it.

642
00:26:55,100 --> 00:26:55,940
Go do your thing.

643
00:26:56,660 --> 00:26:58,560
They're chasing debt to our home.

644
00:26:59,380 --> 00:27:00,900
My home.

645
00:27:00,900 --> 00:27:02,320
Yes, it's your home.

646
00:27:03,500 --> 00:27:04,680
It'll be okay.

647
00:27:05,100 --> 00:27:06,420
- Where's my clothes?
- What clothes?

648
00:27:06,420 --> 00:27:07,260
My coat.

649
00:27:16,580 --> 00:27:17,420
Clean it up.

650
00:27:18,700 --> 00:27:19,680
Be careful on the road.

651
00:27:40,060 --> 00:27:41,280
No money.

652
00:27:41,500 --> 00:27:42,700
Hello.

653
00:27:42,700 --> 00:27:44,120
We're looking for Coach Lu Daxing.

654
00:27:45,620 --> 00:27:46,460
Coach Lu isn't here.

655
00:27:47,780 --> 00:27:49,420
We're from the Xingang Beach Volleyball Team.

656
00:27:49,420 --> 00:27:50,980
Please let him know

657
00:27:50,980 --> 00:27:52,060
we want to hire him

658
00:27:52,060 --> 00:27:54,120
as our head coach.

659
00:27:54,540 --> 00:27:55,380
Okay, got it.

660
00:28:10,780 --> 00:28:11,700
(The Big Player)

661
00:28:14,140 --> 00:28:15,180
You can't do this.

662
00:28:15,180 --> 00:28:16,400
Not bad.

663
00:28:19,780 --> 00:28:21,140
- Come on.
- Join us.

664
00:28:21,140 --> 00:28:22,400
Liqiang.

665
00:28:22,400 --> 00:28:23,630
Come here. I need to tell you something.

666
00:28:23,630 --> 00:28:24,380
What's wrong?

667
00:28:25,140 --> 00:28:26,080
- What's wrong?
- Today,

668
00:28:26,460 --> 00:28:27,740
I got good news

669
00:28:27,740 --> 00:28:29,080
about our beach volleyball team.

670
00:28:29,500 --> 00:28:30,490
- Good news?
- What's wrong?

671
00:28:30,500 --> 00:28:31,600
You're Duoduo's boyfriend now?

672
00:28:32,260 --> 00:28:33,640
Can you be serious?

673
00:28:34,100 --> 00:28:36,300
Remember Coach Lu

674
00:28:36,300 --> 00:28:37,250
from the National Youth Team?

675
00:28:37,700 --> 00:28:39,060
He agreed

676
00:28:39,060 --> 00:28:39,920
to coach us.

677
00:28:40,300 --> 00:28:41,140
What?

678
00:28:41,260 --> 00:28:42,740
National Youth Team coach?

679
00:28:42,740 --> 00:28:43,980
- Yeah.
- Coming to Xingang University

680
00:28:43,980 --> 00:28:45,020
to guide us?

681
00:28:45,020 --> 00:28:45,860
You heard right.

682
00:28:46,100 --> 00:28:47,260
Not bad, Shao Nian.

683
00:28:47,260 --> 00:28:48,740
Didn't think I'd get lucky

684
00:28:48,740 --> 00:28:49,920
in my senior year.

685
00:28:51,100 --> 00:28:51,940
Shao Nian.

686
00:28:52,180 --> 00:28:53,120
How do you know people

687
00:28:53,480 --> 00:28:54,440
from the National Youth Team?

688
00:28:56,380 --> 00:28:58,200
I don't, actually.

689
00:28:58,620 --> 00:29:00,340
But Uncle Li said

690
00:29:00,340 --> 00:29:01,520
he and Coach Lu were partners.

691
00:29:01,980 --> 00:29:03,340
So,

692
00:29:03,340 --> 00:29:04,180
I connected them.

693
00:29:04,380 --> 00:29:06,540
So, it's Duoduo's connections.

694
00:29:06,540 --> 00:29:07,900
You just ran errands.

695
00:29:07,900 --> 00:29:09,020
Without me running around,

696
00:29:09,020 --> 00:29:10,280
he wouldn't agree.

697
00:29:10,580 --> 00:29:11,460
Alright, alright.

698
00:29:11,460 --> 00:29:12,400
You get the credit.

699
00:29:13,460 --> 00:29:14,340
Now it's great.

700
00:29:14,340 --> 00:29:16,020
With the National Youth Team coach,

701
00:29:16,020 --> 00:29:18,000
Yan Xiaojing will win the league for sure.

702
00:29:18,740 --> 00:29:20,760
The recommendation quota
for graduates is settled.

703
00:29:21,820 --> 00:29:22,660
How about this?

704
00:29:22,900 --> 00:29:24,340
I'll get a membership card

705
00:29:24,340 --> 00:29:25,300
at Duoduo's BBQ place

706
00:29:25,300 --> 00:29:26,440
and eat there every day.

707
00:29:27,060 --> 00:29:28,300
You're not getting a card.

708
00:29:28,300 --> 00:29:29,900
You're just looking for a bargain.

709
00:29:29,900 --> 00:29:30,860
I'm boosting

710
00:29:30,860 --> 00:29:32,780
their business.

711
00:29:32,780 --> 00:29:33,740
Right. Stop joking.

712
00:29:33,740 --> 00:29:34,660
Go tell the teacher

713
00:29:34,660 --> 00:29:35,960
to arrange a dorm for Coach Lu.

714
00:29:36,300 --> 00:29:38,120
He can't have nowhere to stay.

715
00:29:39,500 --> 00:29:40,860
Dorm might not be good.

716
00:29:40,860 --> 00:29:42,360
He's the National Youth Team coach.

717
00:29:42,860 --> 00:29:44,520
He might not like it

718
00:29:44,780 --> 00:29:46,080
and not coach us well.

719
00:29:47,700 --> 00:29:49,380
We don't have extra funds

720
00:29:49,380 --> 00:29:50,560
for lodging.

721
00:29:51,740 --> 00:29:53,120
I don't think a coach like him

722
00:29:53,420 --> 00:29:54,400
would mind.

723
00:29:54,860 --> 00:29:55,700
What do you suggest?

724
00:29:58,380 --> 00:29:59,220
Gao.

725
00:29:59,860 --> 00:30:00,720
Think of a solution.

726
00:30:03,020 --> 00:30:03,860
Fine.

727
00:30:04,260 --> 00:30:05,540
The National Youth Team coach coming

728
00:30:05,540 --> 00:30:06,380
is good.

729
00:30:07,620 --> 00:30:09,420
I'll go to the restroom.

730
00:30:09,420 --> 00:30:10,260
You guys talk.

731
00:30:14,340 --> 00:30:15,320
What's up with Gao?

732
00:30:15,820 --> 00:30:16,660
Upset about it?

733
00:30:17,100 --> 00:30:18,280
He seemed fine just now.

734
00:30:19,940 --> 00:30:20,820
I think

735
00:30:20,820 --> 00:30:22,620
he's upset the coach is coming.

736
00:30:22,620 --> 00:30:24,220
His thunder will be stolen.

737
00:30:24,220 --> 00:30:25,300
You're being ridiculous.

738
00:30:25,300 --> 00:30:26,400
Gao isn't like that.

739
00:30:26,980 --> 00:30:28,080
When is Lu Daxing arriving?

740
00:30:28,340 --> 00:30:29,740
Bought the ticket this afternoon.

741
00:30:29,740 --> 00:30:30,580
He'll arrive tomorrow.

742
00:30:30,820 --> 00:30:31,760
That's quick.

743
00:30:32,580 --> 00:30:34,180
He must be short on time,

744
00:30:34,180 --> 00:30:35,360
so he wants it to be quick.

745
00:30:35,780 --> 00:30:37,160
Let's pick him up tomorrow afternoon.

746
00:30:37,540 --> 00:30:38,380
Sure.

747
00:30:40,220 --> 00:30:41,620
The dorm manager was helpful today.

748
00:30:41,620 --> 00:30:42,460
Right.

749
00:30:42,580 --> 00:30:44,160
Thanks to my face.

750
00:30:44,380 --> 00:30:45,300
Oh, please.

751
00:30:45,300 --> 00:30:47,020
Don't forget to buy some fruit

752
00:30:47,020 --> 00:30:48,420
- for the help.
- Got it.

753
00:30:48,420 --> 00:30:50,580
I'll leave it to the current captain's

754
00:30:50,580 --> 00:30:51,960
future boyfriend.

755
00:30:52,300 --> 00:30:53,680
No problem. I'll handle it now.

756
00:30:53,900 --> 00:30:54,740
Come on, Liqiang.

757
00:30:54,860 --> 00:30:56,380
Clean up.

758
00:30:56,380 --> 00:30:57,220
Bye-bye.

759
00:31:00,300 --> 00:31:01,140
That kid.

760
00:31:11,060 --> 00:31:13,160
(Everyone thought I could
join the National Youth Team,)

761
00:31:13,620 --> 00:31:14,560
(including myself.)

762
00:31:15,820 --> 00:31:16,780
(But reality)

763
00:31:16,780 --> 00:31:18,160
(often hits you hardest)

764
00:31:18,420 --> 00:31:19,480
(when you're most confident.)

765
00:31:20,700 --> 00:31:21,560
(That's when I realized)

766
00:31:21,980 --> 00:31:23,040
(I was too naive.)

767
00:31:23,050 --> 00:31:24,680
(National Youth Team Information,
Bulletin Board)

768
00:31:25,060 --> 00:31:26,760
Mom, I made it.

769
00:31:27,140 --> 00:31:28,160
Yes, I made it.

770
00:31:30,460 --> 00:31:31,620
How about you two?

771
00:31:31,620 --> 00:31:32,620
- As expected.
- Not a chance.

772
00:31:32,620 --> 00:31:33,700
Another year wasted.

773
00:31:33,700 --> 00:31:34,560
Try again next year.

774
00:31:35,020 --> 00:31:35,860
Let's see it for you.

775
00:31:35,860 --> 00:31:36,740
Look.

776
00:31:36,740 --> 00:31:38,540
How could he fail?

777
00:31:38,540 --> 00:31:39,420
Impossible.

778
00:31:39,420 --> 00:31:40,880
I saw the teacher nodding.

779
00:31:41,620 --> 00:31:42,480
You're still young.

780
00:31:42,980 --> 00:31:44,300
If you don't make it this time,

781
00:31:44,300 --> 00:31:45,440
there's next time.

782
00:31:46,900 --> 00:31:48,040
I think

783
00:31:48,540 --> 00:31:49,740
you should

784
00:31:49,740 --> 00:31:50,800
go to college first.

785
00:31:51,180 --> 00:31:52,520
After that,

786
00:31:53,100 --> 00:31:55,400
you can switch to sports, right?

787
00:31:57,780 --> 00:31:58,620
Actually,

788
00:31:58,740 --> 00:32:00,280
life has many paths.

789
00:32:00,660 --> 00:32:02,120
If this one doesn't work,

790
00:32:02,580 --> 00:32:04,040
you can take another.

791
00:32:04,500 --> 00:32:07,240
A thousand-mile journey
begins with the first step.

792
00:32:07,540 --> 00:32:08,640
Let's take our time

793
00:32:08,860 --> 00:32:10,680
and live well now.

794
00:32:17,340 --> 00:32:20,620
(Beach Volleyball Activity Room)

795
00:32:26,220 --> 00:32:27,060
Xia.

796
00:32:27,660 --> 00:32:29,100
- No training?
- No.

797
00:32:29,100 --> 00:32:30,740
The new coach is coming.

798
00:32:30,740 --> 00:32:32,200
I'm organizing training plans.

799
00:32:34,300 --> 00:32:35,560
The National Youth Team coach?

800
00:32:37,540 --> 00:32:38,600
Gao told you?

801
00:32:39,540 --> 00:32:41,320
How's that? Exciting, isn't it?

802
00:32:43,380 --> 00:32:44,840
I'm okay.

803
00:32:45,540 --> 00:32:46,720
But Gao Ge

804
00:32:47,700 --> 00:32:49,320
didn't seem excited.

805
00:32:50,980 --> 00:32:51,760
No way.

806
00:32:51,760 --> 00:32:53,060
The National Youth Team coach is coming.

807
00:32:53,060 --> 00:32:53,920
How can he not be excited?

808
00:32:55,420 --> 00:32:56,800
Is something wrong with him?

809
00:32:57,180 --> 00:32:59,080
You know your buddy best.

810
00:33:03,020 --> 00:33:03,860
Xia Liqiang.

811
00:33:04,860 --> 00:33:06,540
Did you ask the teacher for leave?

812
00:33:06,540 --> 00:33:07,920
Yes. What did you do?

813
00:33:09,420 --> 00:33:10,700
What else?

814
00:33:10,700 --> 00:33:12,520
Writing my thesis and training.

815
00:33:13,060 --> 00:33:13,940
The team

816
00:33:13,940 --> 00:33:15,200
isn't training, right?

817
00:33:15,420 --> 00:33:17,300
Can't I train extra?

818
00:33:17,300 --> 00:33:19,060
The Seven-School League

819
00:33:19,060 --> 00:33:20,900
is important to me.

820
00:33:20,900 --> 00:33:22,460
I'm dedicated. Okay?

821
00:33:22,460 --> 00:33:23,300
Fine.

822
00:33:23,340 --> 00:33:24,360
Listen.

823
00:33:24,820 --> 00:33:25,780
Do you know Coach Lu Daxing

824
00:33:25,780 --> 00:33:27,300
from the National Youth Team

825
00:33:27,300 --> 00:33:28,660
is coming to guide us?

826
00:33:28,660 --> 00:33:30,240
The National Youth Team coach?

827
00:33:30,700 --> 00:33:31,900
You're joking.

828
00:33:31,900 --> 00:33:33,400
Why would he come to Xingang?

829
00:33:33,940 --> 00:33:35,660
Why not?

830
00:33:35,660 --> 00:33:37,640
Xingang is a hidden gem.

831
00:33:38,260 --> 00:33:40,480
Our players have huge potential for their team.

832
00:33:41,260 --> 00:33:43,040
Just Chen Weilan. Who else?

833
00:33:44,940 --> 00:33:46,480
Me and Gao.

834
00:33:48,100 --> 00:33:49,940
Who and Gao? I didn't hear it.

835
00:33:49,940 --> 00:33:51,540
Me and Gao.

836
00:33:51,540 --> 00:33:53,200
Stop teasing.

837
00:33:54,460 --> 00:33:57,140
A National Youth Team coach coming

838
00:33:57,140 --> 00:33:58,100
isn't exciting?

839
00:33:58,100 --> 00:33:59,380
It's exciting.

840
00:33:59,380 --> 00:34:00,800
It's the National Youth Team coach.

841
00:34:01,100 --> 00:34:02,100
How long is he staying?

842
00:34:02,100 --> 00:34:03,680
Just sightseeing?

843
00:34:04,100 --> 00:34:04,940
You

844
00:34:05,180 --> 00:34:06,500
are overthinking.

845
00:34:06,500 --> 00:34:08,300
He's the National Youth Team coach.

846
00:34:08,300 --> 00:34:10,420
Even a day's guidance

847
00:34:10,420 --> 00:34:12,440
helps with our skills.

848
00:34:13,940 --> 00:34:15,700
I envy your optimism.

849
00:34:15,700 --> 00:34:17,640
Always happy.

850
00:34:18,050 --> 00:34:19,220
Do all women

851
00:34:19,220 --> 00:34:20,710
like to tell people off like this?

852
00:34:21,340 --> 00:34:22,980
All women?

853
00:34:22,980 --> 00:34:24,700
Besides me and your mom,

854
00:34:24,700 --> 00:34:25,800
what other women do you have?

855
00:34:26,090 --> 00:34:27,700
No, don't be so suspicious,

856
00:34:27,700 --> 00:34:28,540
okay?

857
00:34:28,980 --> 00:34:30,420
Are you going to tell me or not?

858
00:34:30,420 --> 00:34:31,700
Which woman told you off?

859
00:34:31,700 --> 00:34:32,820
Tell me. Tell me.

860
00:34:32,820 --> 00:34:33,670
Chen Weilan.

861
00:34:34,090 --> 00:34:35,180
Chen Weilan?

862
00:34:35,180 --> 00:34:36,670
She said I don't care about Gao.

863
00:34:37,570 --> 00:34:38,860
But actually, Gao

864
00:34:38,860 --> 00:34:40,260
seems to have tried out

865
00:34:40,260 --> 00:34:41,480
for the National Youth Team before.

866
00:34:42,090 --> 00:34:42,930
Really?

867
00:34:43,380 --> 00:34:45,080
I don't think Gao Ge

868
00:34:45,080 --> 00:34:46,220
