876
00:35:02,100 --> 00:35:02,960
That's a good thing.

877
00:35:03,340 --> 00:35:04,520
Who invited him?

878
00:35:04,860 --> 00:35:05,840
Shao Nian did.

879
00:35:06,100 --> 00:35:07,520
