948
00:37:39,020 --> 00:37:40,700
He wants to surprise her.

949
00:37:40,700 --> 00:37:42,090
We can't spoil the surprise.

950
00:37:42,220 --> 00:37:43,120
Got it.

951
00:37:43,420 --> 00:37:46,160
Shao Nian is really sweet to Duoduo.

952
00:37:46,540 --> 00:37:48,620
The three of them will pick up Coach Lu.

953
00:37:48,620 --> 00:37:50,400
We'll stay here and wait for Duoduo.

954
00:37:51,620 --> 00:37:52,460
Alright then.

955
00:37:53,180 --> 00:37:54,400
