990
00:39:01,500 --> 00:39:02,900
at Xingang University too.

991
00:39:02,900 --> 00:39:03,900
So,

992
00:39:03,900 --> 00:39:05,120
he's our senior.

993
00:39:08,660 --> 00:39:09,500
Got it.

994
00:39:10,700 --> 00:39:11,640
Thanks, bro.

995
00:39:12,220 --> 00:39:14,100
Your contributions to the team

996
00:39:14,100 --> 00:39:14,960
will never be forgotten.

997
00:39:16,900 --> 00:39:17,960
Don't flatter yourself.

998
00:39:18,340 --> 00:39:19,740
He's not doing it for you.

999
00:39:19,740 --> 00:39:21,880
He's doing it for the captain.

1000
00:39:23,620 --> 00:39:24,460
