1001
00:39:25,100 --> 00:39:26,140
Don't distract the driver

1002
00:39:26,140 --> 00:39:27,280
while driving.

1003
00:39:40,220 --> 00:39:41,060
Hello?

1004
00:39:42,100 --> 00:39:43,040
This is Lu Daxing.

1005
00:39:43,500 --> 00:39:44,340
Coach Lu.

1006
00:39:44,420 --> 00:39:45,500
We're on our way

1007
00:39:45,500 --> 00:39:46,440
