1008
00:39:46,700 --> 00:39:47,540
Go ahead.

1009
00:39:48,540 --> 00:39:49,580
There's no need to pick me up.

1010
00:39:49,580 --> 00:39:50,880
I'm already at your school's entrance.

1011
00:39:51,420 --> 00:39:52,960
You're already there?

1012
00:39:53,460 --> 00:39:54,300
Yes.

1013
00:39:54,480 --> 00:39:55,520
Just come to the school entrance

1014
00:39:55,520 --> 00:39:56,260
to pick me up.

1015
00:39:56,500 --> 00:39:57,600
Alright then.

1016
00:39:58,940 --> 00:40:00,440
He's arrived at the school?

1017
00:40:00,660 --> 00:40:01,760
Let's head back to the school.

1018
00:40:04,340 --> 00:40:05,600
We came all this way for nothing.

1019
00:40:22,820 --> 00:40:24,400
Didn't he say he was at the school entrance?

1020
00:40:24,980 --> 00:40:26,160
I'll call and ask.

1021
00:40:26,820 --> 00:40:28,280
Can't tell who it is.

1022
00:40:37,780 --> 00:40:38,620
Well.

1023
00:40:44,540 --> 00:40:45,390
Hello?

1024
00:40:45,410 --> 00:40:46,960
