Staying in the dorms, huh?

1045
00:41:21,220 --> 00:41:22,060
Yeah.

1046
00:41:23,020 --> 00:41:23,860
Well.

1047
00:41:24,020 --> 00:41:25,300
Staying on campus is nice too.

1048
00:41:25,300 --> 00:41:27,020
A bit nostalgic. I like it.

1049
00:41:27,020 --> 00:41:27,900
Sorry about that, Coach.

1050
00:41:27,900 --> 00:41:29,560
