1051
00:41:30,100 --> 00:41:30,940
No need.

1052
00:41:31,260 --> 00:41:32,180
Since I'm here to work

1053
00:41:32,180 --> 00:41:33,500
with the beach volleyball team,

1054
00:41:33,500 --> 00:41:34,940
I should go

1055
00:41:34,940 --> 00:41:36,060
to see the team first.

1056
00:41:36,060 --> 00:41:37,300
- Alright.
- Okay.

1057
00:41:37,300 --> 00:41:38,700
- Let's go.
- Off we go.

1058
00:41:38,700 --> 00:41:40,140
- Let's get in the car.
- The luggage.

1059
00:41:40,140 --> 00:41:41,100
I'll take care of it.

1060
00:41:41,100 --> 00:41:42,380
Nice car you've got there.

1061
00:41:42,380 --> 00:41:44,080
