1071
00:42:05,500 --> 00:42:07,520
I'll make a good impression.

1072
00:42:07,900 --> 00:42:09,160
What about your Longlong?

1073
00:42:09,660 --> 00:42:11,220
We've been training

1074
00:42:11,220 --> 00:42:12,920
