1078
00:42:19,420 --> 00:42:20,860
We'll just keep going on our own.

1079
00:42:20,860 --> 00:42:22,320
Keep pushing forward.

1080
00:42:23,900 --> 00:42:24,860
Everyone,

1081
00:42:24,860 --> 00:42:26,900
I have some good news.

1082
00:42:26,900 --> 00:42:28,440
Come on, Duoduo, Weilan, have a seat.

1083
00:42:28,740 --> 00:42:29,880
What's the good news?

1084
00:42:30,700 --> 00:42:31,960
You'll know in a moment.

1085
00:42:32,700 --> 00:42:34,340
