1087
00:42:36,220 --> 00:42:37,140
Come on.

1088
00:42:37,140 --> 00:42:38,480
Let me introduce everyone.

1089
00:42:41,180 --> 00:42:42,020
This is

1090
00:42:42,220 --> 00:42:44,500
the coach from the National Youth Team.

1091
00:42:44,500 --> 00:42:45,760
Lu Daxing.

1092
00:42:45,980 --> 00:42:46,940
Lu Daxing.

1093
00:42:46,940 --> 00:42:48,000
Everyone, let's welcome him.

1094
